commentable_entity.title: Boycott All Future Pirates of the Caribbean Movies That Do Not Include Johnny Depp
commentable_entity.description: Disney fired Johnny Depp, whose character Captain Jack Sparrow is the heart and soul of the entire Pirates of the Caribbean franchise. They did this based on the fallacious hit piece Amber Heard wrote in the Washington Post in 2018, accusing Johnny Depp of domestic abuse. She did this to ruin him and further her own career, after she abused him physically and verbally for years. Show your support for Johnny Depp and the truth by refusing to watch any further Pirates movies made by Disney.
commentable_entity.letter_body: Boycott All Future Pirates of the Caribbean Movies That Do Not Include Johnny Depp

comment: There is no other Captain Jack Sparrow than Johnny Depp! He’s been wrongly vilified. Disney needs to make this right. He’s brought so much joy to fans with his surprise appearances at the parks and hospitals. You didn’t just rob him of the role, you robbed his fans, especially children of their hero. Start buying up alpacas and name it Sparrow’s Alpaca Sanctuary in honor of Johnny! HE made the movies. Without him, they would have been mediocre at best.
